syntax=> newlist=filter(filter_function,oldlist) ->>>>Every element is passed through the filter function and if it return true then passed through the newlist :)

l=[1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9,0]
def iseven(x):
    if(x%2==0):
        return True
    else:
        return False

lnew=list(filter(iseven,l))
print(lnew)
   
